    <abstract id="aspace_78425ec55120f8af3f970a8ecef352c6">The Time Inc. <title render="italic">Money</title> Editorial Records: Managing Editor Marshall Loeb Files focus on  public appearances made by Loeb while he was managing editor. The collection is primarily scripts and transcripts.</abstract>
